V0.0.1 2019/12/31
------------------------
+ improves
	- App title and version as constants
	- showing current file opened in app title
	- Copy/Cut disabled if we have no selected text
	- style: textbox background colour, menus with tearoff=0 option, flat menu style...
+ bugs
	- popup now disapears when mouse left-clicking out
+ licensing:
	- upgraded to GPLv3+
	- correct license headers, and licensing practises
+ coding style:
	- adopted PEP8
	- imports are clearer now

